(** 
   The user interface for the system. 

   When the system starts, the user will be prompted to create a profile by 
   answering a series of questions through the command line. 

   The user will be placed in a waiting room until matches are found. 

   The user will see a list of matches and can select which user to chat with by 
   typing in a name. 

   The user will enter a chat room and speak with a match until the command 
   "quit" is typed. The system will exit on the "quit" command. 
